== 系統新增功能 ==

=== 使用者介面 ===
{{see also|扁平化设计}}在蘋果設計高級副總裁[[乔纳森·埃维|強納生·艾夫]]的主導下，iOS 7採用了全新的的視覺設計，整體風格由[[iOS_6|iOS 6]]以前的[[仿制品|擬物風格]]改為[[扁平化设计|扁平化風格]]，並對使用者介面進行全面的改造，包括[[字體|字體]]更加纖細精緻、[[過場_(動畫)|過場動畫]]更加平順流暢、應用程式的圖示更加清晰銳利等<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":6" />。據強納生表示：「恆久深刻的美，呈現在簡潔、清晰、效率之上。真正的簡潔不是只除去一切雜亂及裝飾，而是要為複雜性帶來秩序。iOS 7 明確地呈現這些目標。它有著全新的架構，以協調一致的方式橫跨整個系統的應用。」<ref name="Verge_Apple_announces" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2013/06/10/ios-7-announced/|title=Apple shows off completely redesigned iOS 7 at WWDC, coming this fall|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-06-10|last=Heater|first=Brian|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230001621/https://www.engadget.com/2013/06/10/ios-7-announced/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== AirDrop ===
{{see also|隔空投送}}[[AirDrop|AirDrop]]檔案傳輸功能於[[Mac_OS_X_Lion|Mac OS X Lion]]中出現，並於iOS 7首次引入[[iOS|iOS]]中。用戶可在控制中心或分享選單中點選AirDrop功能，透過[[Wi-Fi直连|Wi-Fi直连]]技術將照片、影片等檔案與附近的iOS裝置用户共享<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204144|title=在 iPhone、iPad 或 iPod touch 上使用 AirDrop|newspaper=Apple Support|accessdate=2018-07-31|language=zh-TW|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180731030052/https://support.apple.com/zh-tw/HT204144|archive-date=2018-07-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/getting-to-know-airdrop-on-ios-7/|title=Getting to know AirDrop on iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-09-23|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230085749/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/getting-to-know-airdrop-on-ios-7/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於硬體機能因素，AirDrop功能只能在[[iPhone_5|iPhone 5]]、[[IPod_touch_(第五代)|第五代iPod touch]]、[[IPad_(第四代)|第四代iPad]]、[[IPad_mini|第一代iPad mini]]及更新机型上使用<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140827040854/http://www.apple.com/tw/ios/whats-new/|title=Apple - iOS 7 - 全新功能|accessdate=2018-07-31|date=2014-08-27}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.todaysiphone.com/2014/03/use-airdrop-ios-7/|title=How To: Use AirDrop in iOS 7|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2014-03-11|last=Oram|first=Adam|publisher=PhoneDog|website=Today's iPhone|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218231541/http://www.todaysiphone.com/2014/03/use-airdrop-ios-7/|archive-date=2017-02-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 控制中心 ===
{{see also|控制中心 (iOS)}}iOS 7首次引入[[控制中心_(iOS)|控制中心]]功能，用户可在任何情況下，從螢幕畫面底部向上滑動手指以開啟控制中心介面<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" />。控制中心提供了常用的系統功能調整與開關，包括[[飛航模式|飛航模式]]、[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]、[[藍牙|藍牙]]、[[勿扰模式|勿扰模式]]及锁定屏幕旋转等<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":9">{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/18/ios-7-how-to-use-control-center-to-quickly-manage-settings/|title=iOS 7 How-to: Use Control Center to quickly manage settings|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-09-18|last=Guarino|first=Sarah|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220185802/https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/18/ios-7-how-to-use-control-center-to-quickly-manage-settings/|archive-date=2016-12-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Camera app">{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/20/how-to-use-the-new-camera-app-in-ios-7/|title=How-to: Use the new Camera app in iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-09-20|last=Guarino|first=Sarah|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230090052/https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/20/how-to-use-the-new-camera-app-in-ios-7/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，也可以調整螢幕亮度、播放或暫停音樂、控制手電筒、開啓计时器、计算器和相機<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":9" /><ref name="Camera app" />。需要注意的是，置於控制中心的快捷鍵可能會因為機型的不同而有所變化<ref name=":8" />。

=== 通知中心 ===
{{see also|通知中心}}在iOS 7中，通知中心的介面經過重新設計，由原本的一體化改為三標籤頁風格。新版通知中心分為今天、全部通知和未讀通知三種類別，用户可透過左右滑動切換分類。新加入的「今天」標籤能提供天氣預報和行事曆通知，統整今日大小事。另外，通知現在也會出現在鎖定畫面上，讓用戶在鎖定畫面就能看見所有通知<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2013/6/10/4413228/apple-wwdc-2013-everything-you-need-to-know|title=Apple debuts iOS 7, OS X Mavericks, and new Macs: everything you need to know|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-06-10|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6HHTvV3Lx?url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/10/4413228/apple-wwdc-2013-everything-you-need-to-know|archive-date=2013-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2048936/get-to-know-ios-7-notification-center.html|title=Get to know iOS 7: Notification Center|accessdate=2017-02-05|date=2013-09-18|last=Friedman|first=Lex|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507114653/http://www.macworld.com/article/2048936/get-to-know-ios-7-notification-center.html|archive-date=2017-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 多工處理 ===
iOS 7引入了背景應用程式自動整理功能，能夠自動依據手機的電力和網路狀況更新背景應用程式，不需再透過開啓應用程式來手動更新內容<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" />。此外，多工處理介面也獲得更新，加入了預覽功能<ref name=":8" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/18/ios-7-how-to-use-the-new-multitasking-interface/|title=iOS 7 How-to: Use the new multitasking interface|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-18|last=Guarino|first=Sarah|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231075032/https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/18/ios-7-how-to-use-the-new-multitasking-interface/|archive-date=2016-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2048935/get-to-know-ios-7-multitasking.html|title=Get to know iOS 7: Multitasking|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-18|last=Moren|first=Dan|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161122074302/http://www.macworld.com/article/2048935/get-to-know-ios-7-multitasking.html|archive-date=2016-11-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== CarPlay ===
{{see also|CarPlay}}[[CarPlay|CarPlay]]（原名iOS in the Car，即車用版iOS）功能首次於iOS 7.1更新引入，使用戶可透過汽車車載系統使用iOS裝置的各項功能，包括播放音樂、接收與傳送簡訊及定位導航等<ref name=":8" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2014/03/10/apple-releases-ios-7-1/|title=Apple releases iOS 7.1 with CarPlay support|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2014-03-10|last=Molen|first=Brad|publisher=[[AOL|AOL]]|website=[[Engadget|Engadget]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230230501/https://www.engadget.com/2014/03/10/apple-releases-ios-7-1/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此功能只支援使用[[Lightning接头|Lightning]]接頭的裝置<ref>{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2014/03/03/apple-rebrands-ios-in-the-car-as-carplay-compatible-vehicles-launching-later-this-year/|title=Apple rebrands iOS in the Car as CarPlay, compatible vehicles launching later this year|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2014-03-03|last=Mayo|first=Benjamin|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230231418/https://9to5mac.com/2014/03/03/apple-rebrands-ios-in-the-car-as-carplay-compatible-vehicles-launching-later-this-year/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Siri ===
{{see also|Siri}}Siri的介面全面更新，新增過場動畫，並改以音波的流動表示Siri正在傾聽用戶說話<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" />。除了新的介面外，Siri也更換了其使用的聲音，並可選擇使用女性和男性的聲音。此外，Siri亦新增了控制系統設定的功能，例如開關藍牙、Wi-Fi或調整螢幕亮度等。[[Bing|Bing]]成為Siri的預設搜尋引擎，同時[[推特|推特]]及[[維基百科|維基百科]]也整合至Siri中<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2048736/get-to-know-ios-7-siri.html|title=Get to know iOS 7: Siri|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-18|last=Caldwell|first=Serenity|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161207033048/http://www.macworld.com/article/2048736/get-to-know-ios-7-siri.html|archive-date=2016-12-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 其它功能 ===
在iOS 7中，[[Spotlight|Spotlight]]搜尋現在也可以於主畫面時，藉由從螢幕偏上方處向下拉存取<ref name=":7" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imore.com/how-to-access-use-spotlight-seach-iphone-ipad|title=How to access and use Spotlight search on your iPhone or iPad|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-18|last=Kazmucka|first=Allyson|website=[[iMore|iMore]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230231543/http://www.imore.com/how-to-access-use-spotlight-seach-iphone-ipad|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.laptopmag.com/articles/how-to-use-spotlight-search-in-ios-7|title=How to Use Spotlight Search in iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-20|last=Andronico|first=Michael|website=LaptopMag|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221225333/http://www.laptopmag.com/articles/how-to-use-spotlight-search-in-ios-7|archive-date=2016-12-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

iOS 7首次引進「視角」桌布功能，當選用視角功能時，應用程式圖示會隨裝置傾斜角度而移動，製造圖示浮在桌布上的[[錯覺|錯覺]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2013/09/parallax-and-the-ios-7-wallpaper/|title=Parallax and the iOS 7 Wallpaper|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-26|last=Allain|first=Rhett|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(website)|Wired]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230230429/https://www.wired.com/2013/09/parallax-and-the-ios-7-wallpaper/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在iOS 7中，新安裝或更新之後仍未開啟的應用程式名稱旁邊，現在會出現小藍點以供識別<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/five-quick-ios-7-mysteries-solved/|title=Five quick iOS 7 mysteries solved|accessdate=2017-05-23|date=2013-09-20|last=Broida|first=Rick|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171016173924/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/five-quick-ios-7-mysteries-solved/|archive-date=2017-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在iOS 7中，資料夾功能得到了擴充，引入與主畫面相似的分頁機制，使一個資料夾能容納的程式數量遽增至135個<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lifewire.com/how-many-apps-allowed-iphone-2000752|title=How Many Apps and Folders Can an iPhone Have?|accessdate=2017-10-15|date=2017-03-20|last=Costello|first=Sam|publisher=[[Dotdash|Dotdash]]|website=[[Lifewire|Lifewire]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806182301/https://www.lifewire.com/how-many-apps-allowed-iphone-2000752|archive-date=2017-08-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

iOS 7新增電話阻擋功能，能可阻止特定人士的聯繫，範圍包括電話、FaceTime與訊息應用程式<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/09/19/ios-7-feature-focus-block-calls-texts-and-facetimes-from-individual-numbers|title=iOS 7 feature focus: Block calls, texts, and FaceTimes from individual numbers|accessdate=2017-02-05|date=2013-09-19|last=Bostic|first=Kevin|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206022232/http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/09/19/ios-7-feature-focus-block-calls-texts-and-facetimes-from-individual-numbers|archive-date=2017-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 應用程式新增功能 ==

=== App Store ===
在iOS 7中，應用程式商店[[App_Store_(iOS)|App Store]]獲得許多重大更新，包括介面的重新設計；自動更新應用程式功能的引入<ref name=":7" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/09/18/ios-7-feature-focus-app-store-auto-updates-and-itunes-radio|title=iOS 7 feature focus: App Store auto-updates and iTunes Radio|accessdate=2017-07-20|date=2013-09-18|last=Cole|first=Shane|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206174757/http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/09/18/ios-7-feature-focus-app-store-auto-updates-and-itunes-radio|archive-date=2017-02-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theverge.com/2013/6/10/4415588/app-store-automatic-updates-ios-7-apple-wwdc-2013|title=App Store will update apps automatically in iOS 7|accessdate=2017-07-20|date=2013-06-10|last=Kastrenakes|first=Jacob|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170205081806/http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/10/4415588/app-store-automatic-updates-ios-7-apple-wwdc-2013|archive-date=2017-02-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>；新加入的「附近」標籤，能自動依據用戶所在地推薦應用程式<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.idownloadblog.com/2014/04/19/app-store-guide/|title=iOS 7: the ultimate App Store guide|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2014-04-19|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|website=iDownloadBlog|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230090122/http://www.idownloadblog.com/2014/04/19/app-store-guide/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>；下載舊版應用程式功能，能在系統不支援最新版本應用程式時，自動選擇最新的相容版本下載<ref>{{cite web|url=http://mashable.com/2013/09/17/ios-legacy-apps/|title=Apple App Store Introduces Legacy App Download Option|accessdate=2016-12-31|date=2013-09-17|last=Ulanoff|first=Lance|website=[[Mashable|Mashable]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101091001/http://mashable.com/2013/09/17/ios-legacy-apps/|archive-date=2017-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== Safari ===
{{see also|Safari}}在iOS 7中，內建瀏覽器[[Safari|Safari]]獲得許多重大更新。搜尋欄與網址欄整合為智慧搜尋欄；網址列和工具列在瀏覽頁面時將自動隱藏；新增了翻頁手勢，用户可從畫面邊緣滑動來前後翻頁。此外，還新增了不留下追蹤紀錄的隱私瀏覽模式和翻頁效果的標籤頁瀏覽模式<ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/four-features-to-know-about-in-safari-on-ios-7/|title=Four features to know about in Safari on iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-30|date=2013-09-19|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230231205/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/four-features-to-know-about-in-safari-on-ios-7/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 相機與相片 ===
iOS 7於相機應用程式內新增「正方形」模式，能拍攝與社群媒體[[Instagram|Instagram]]相似的相片，並加入了多種濾鏡<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" /><ref name=":8" /><ref name="Camera app2">{{cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/20/how-to-use-the-new-camera-app-in-ios-7/|title=How-to: Use the new Camera app in iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-09-20|last=Guarino|first=Sarah|website=9to5Mac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230090052/https://9to5mac.com/2013/09/20/how-to-use-the-new-camera-app-in-ios-7/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>；「連拍」模式，按住拍攝按鈕，就能以每秒10張的速率拍攝相片<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cnet.com/how-to/five-tips-for-the-new-camera-app-on-ios-7/|title=Five tips for the new Camera app on iOS 7|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-09-18|last=Cipriani|first=Jason|publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]]|website=[[CNET|CNET]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230160258/https://www.cnet.com/how-to/five-tips-for-the-new-camera-app-on-ios-7/|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>；[[iPhone_5s|iPhone 5s]]專用的「[[慢动作|慢動作]]」模式，能以每秒120格的高[[帧率|幀率]]錄製影片，並可以在相片應用程式編輯慢動作的起迄點<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/apple/how-use-slo-mo-iphone-5s-make-slow-motion-videos-iphone-3481480/|title=How to use Slo-Mo in iPhone 5s: make slow-motion videos on iPhone|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2013-11-08|last=Macro|first=Ashleigh|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219013600/http://www.macworld.co.uk/how-to/apple/how-use-slo-mo-iphone-5s-make-slow-motion-videos-iphone-3481480/|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>；其它更新包括重新設計的介面、在錄影過程中可以使用手指縮放[[變焦鏡|變焦]]等<ref name=":1" /><ref name=":7" />。

相片應用程式則經過重新設計，改為「相片」、「分享」及「相簿」等三標籤頁形式；相片除了以「時間」排序，還可以「年份」、「選集」或新加入的「時刻」模式排序。在「時刻」分類中，相片將會依照拍攝時間與地點歸類為不同的「時刻」<ref name=":8" /><ref name=":10">{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2048867/get-to-know-ios-7-camera-and-photos.html|title=Get to know iOS 7: Camera and Photos|accessdate=2016-12-31|date=2013-09-19|last=Caldwell|first=Serenity|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101002733/http://www.macworld.com/article/2048867/get-to-know-ios-7-camera-and-photos.html|archive-date=2017-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。相片串流功能現在正式支援影片的分享，共享相片串流相簿中首次支援讓其它的用户上傳相片或影片檔案<ref name=":8" />。此外，相片應用程式還新增了[[隔空投送|AirDrop]]分享選項<ref name=":10" />。

=== 音樂 ===
{{see also|iTunes Radio}}iOS 7中的音樂應用程式整合了[[iTunes_Radio|iTunes Radio]]功能。iTunes Radio是一個免費音樂串流服務，用户可以從內建的電台中選擇，或是以歌手、歌曲或專輯來建立自訂的電台。iTunes Radio中將會穿插廣告，但[[iTunes_Match|iTunes Match]]服務用戶將可以在無廣告的環境下使用<ref name=":7" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.wired.com/2013/06/apple-dials-in-itunes-radi|title=Apple Dials in iTunes Radio, a New Streaming Music Service|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2013-06-10|last=Baldwin|first=Roberto|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Wired_(website)|Wired]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230155817/https://www.wired.com/2013/06/apple-dials-in-itunes-radi|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年，iTunes Radio正式由[[Apple_Music|Apple Music]]取代<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/3023410/streaming-services/apple-drops-free-itunes-radio-bundles-it-into-apple-music.html|title=Apple drops free iTunes Radio, bundles it into Apple Music|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2016-01-16|last=Mediati|first=Nick|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230160245/http://www.macworld.com/article/3023410/streaming-services/apple-drops-free-itunes-radio-bundles-it-into-apple-music.html|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/01/29/apple-merges-itunes-radio-channels-into-apple-music-beats-1-now-lone-free-to-stream-service|title=Apple merges iTunes Radio channels into Apple Music, Beats 1 now lone free-to-stream service|accessdate=2016-12-29|date=2016-01-28|last=Campbell|first=Mikey|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161230160118/http://appleinsider.com/articles/16/01/29/apple-merges-itunes-radio-channels-into-apple-music-beats-1-now-lone-free-to-stream-service|archive-date=2016-12-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 地圖 ===
{{see also|蘋果地圖}}蘋果地圖現在支援步驟式導航<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.macworld.com/article/2144604/33-great-tips-and-tricks-for-ios-7.html|title=33 great tips and tricks for iOS 7|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2014-04-17|publisher=[[International_Data_Group|International Data Group]]|first1=Serenity|last1=Caldwell|first2=Dan|last2=Moren|website=[[Macworld|Macworld]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219114732/http://www.macworld.com/article/2144604/33-great-tips-and-tricks-for-ios-7.html|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蘋果地圖的介面也獲得更新，新增了全螢幕模式，啟用全螢幕模式時導覽列及搜尋欄皆會自動隱藏；夜晚模式，於日落後自動啟用<ref name=":1" />。此外，現在在地圖內還新增了語音助理[[Siri|Siri]]的音量調整選項，以免Siri的聲音蓋過導航指示<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/07/12/ios-7-maps-go-full-screen-navigation-gets-night-mode-new-siri-options|title=iOS 7 Maps go full screen, navigation gets night mode, new Siri options|accessdate=2017-02-18|date=2013-07-12|last=Dilger|first=Daniel Eran|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170219095041/http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/07/12/ios-7-maps-go-full-screen-navigation-gets-night-mode-new-siri-options|archive-date=2017-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 天氣 ===
在iOS 7中，天氣應用程式獲得全新視覺設計，背景動畫化，以表示現在的天氣情況；應用程式圖示也經過更新<ref>{{cite web|url=http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/06/18/inside-ios-7-apples-weather-app-gets-animated|title=Inside iOS 7: Apple's Weather app gets animated|accessdate=2016-12-31|date=2013-06-18|last=Hughes|first=Neil|website=AppleInsider|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170101001227/http://appleinsider.com/articles/13/06/18/inside-ios-7-apples-weather-app-gets-animated|archive-date=2017-01-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

